{"tid":1583081,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[20/9] 馬會7間場外投注處明關閉","createTime":"2019-09-20T12:06:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T14:47:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"87f058ffd98306b102c8054f92f48e47eaa5c8d3","tid":1583081,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:06:09.000Z","msg":"馬會表示考慮到最新情況，為確保顧客及員工的安全，部分場外投注處明日（21日）暫停服務或提早關閉，並會密切留意有關情況，以決定是否需要暫時關閉其他場外投注處。市民可使用其他投注渠道或前往其他地區的場外投注處。<br />\n<br />\n明日暫停服務的場外投注處為：屯門市廣場、元朗合益路、元朗泰衡街、北角電氣道、沙田好運中心、粉嶺名都及荃灣青山道；另元朗青山公路場外投注處將於明日下午6時關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190920/s00001/1568979458259/%e9%a6%ac%e6%9c%837%e9%96%93%e5%a0%b4%e5%a4%96%e6%8a%95%e6%b3%a8%e8%99%95%e6%98%8e%e9%97%9c%e9%96%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190920%2Fs00001%2F1568979458259%2F%25e9%25a6%25ac%25e6%259c%25837%25e9%2596%2593%25e5%25a0%25b4%25e5%25a4%2596%25e6%258a%2595%25e6%25b3%25a8%25e8%2599%2595%25e6%2598%258e%25e9%2597%259c%25e9%2596%2589&d=2aT02SOmMwK2whwg3zZG1w8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=e068ba5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190920%2Fs00001%2F1568979458259%2F%25e9%25a6%25ac%25e6%259c%25837%25e9%2596%2593%25e5%25a0%25b4%25e5%25a4%2596%25e6%258a%2595%25e6%25b3%25a8%25e8%2599%2595%25e6%2598%258e%25e9%2597%259c%25e9%2596%2589&h=22ccc717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190920/s00001/1568979458259/%e9%a6%ac%e6%9c%837%e9%96%93%e5%a0%b4%e5%a4%96%e6%8a%95%e6%b3%a8%e8%99%95%e6%98%8e%e9%97%9c%e9%96%89</a>"},{"pid":"a409639d0797ccad6967d9bef0ce6c9f37e55fd3","tid":1583081,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T12:07:00.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link tar